                    <div class="announcement-badge">Urgent</div>
                    <h3>Water Maintenance Schedule</h3>
                    <p class="announcement-meta">
                        <i class="bi bi-clock"></i> Posted 2 hours ago
                        <span class="badge bg-danger ms-2">Important</span>
                    </p>
                    <p>Water supply will be temporarily suspended on March 5, 2025, from 10 AM to 4 PM due to scheduled maintenance work.</p>
                    <div class="announcement-footer">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Regular Announcements -->
                <div class="announcement-card">
                    <h3>Monthly Community Meeting</h3>
                    <p class="announcement-meta">
                        <i class="bi bi-clock"></i> Posted 1 day ago
                        <span class="badge bg-info ms-2">Event</span>
                    </p>
                    <p>Join us for our monthly community meeting on March 10, 2025, at 7 PM in the Function Hall.</p>
                    <div class="announcement-footer">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="announcement-card">
                    <h3>New Security Protocol Implementation</h3>
                    <p class="announcement-meta">
                        <i class="bi bi-clock"></i> Posted 3 days ago
                        <span class="badge bg-success ms-2">Update</span>
                    </p>
                    <p>Starting March 15, 2025, we will be implementing new security protocols for visitor entry.</p>
                    <div class="announcement-footer">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar with Calendar and Polls -->
        <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="sidebar-widget calendar-widget">
                <h3>Upcoming Events</h3>
                <div class="mini-calendar">
                    <div class="calendar-event">
                        <div class="event-date">
                            <span class="date">5</span>
                            <span class="month">MAR</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="event-details">
                            <h4>Water Maintenance</h4>
                            <p>10:00 AM - 4:00 PM</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="calendar-event">
                        <div class="event-date">
                            <span class="date">10</span>
                            <span class="month">MAR</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="event-details">
                            <h4>Community Meeting</h4>
                            <p>7:00 PM - 9:00 PM</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="calendar-event">
                        <div class="event-date">
                            <span class="date">15</span>
                            <span class="month">MAR</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="event-details">
                            <h4>Security Update</h4>
                            <p>New protocols begin</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button class="btn btn-primary w-100 mt-3">View Full Calendar</button>
            </div>

